question: Dina taun naon 'net cash used in working capital' ngalakukeun pangaruh nu paling negatip kana cash flow?
Hitung jumlah total 'net cash provided by operating activities' kanggo sababaraha wektu anu dicatetkeun dina tabel (2011-2013).
Apa 'net income adjusted to reconcile net income to net cash provided by operating activities1' dina warsa anu ngagaduhan 'net cash provided by operating activities' paling luhur?
Analisa trend taun ka taun tina 'net cash provided by operating activities' tina taun 2011 ka 2013.
answer: Hiji 'net cash provided by operating activities' nyieun trend positif anu konsisten jeung kuat dina periode tilu taun. Ieu naek tina $273.5 dina taun 2011 ka $357.2 dina taun 2012, terus naék signifikan ka $592.9 dina taun 2013, nu ngajelaskeun kalayan kualitas kas operasional nu makin ningkat tiap taun.

question: Sasaran taun nu mana 'net cash ( used in ) provided by financing activities' mangrupa negatif sareng 'net cash used in investing activities' ogé negatif leuwih ti $100?

Gaduh taun 2013, porséna ti 'net income adjusted to reconcile net income to net cash provided by operating activities1' anu dirobah jadi 'net cash provided by operating activities'? Nyatakeun ieu dina persén, dibulatkeun kana dua tempat desimal.

Ayaana 'net cash provided by operating activities' diitung salaku jumlah tina tilu baris kawung, naon nilaana dina 2012 lamun 'net cash used in working capital' ngalaman 50% leuwih leutik negatif (misalna -$146.6)?

Berdasarekeun data tina taun 2011 ka 2013, pikeun sahiji hubungan nu jelas antara 'net income adjusted...' jeung 'net cash provided by operating activities'? Apa pendapatan diadjustkeun leuwih luhur pasti ngahasilkeun kas leuwih luhur tina operasi?
answer: Henteu, pendapatan diadjustkeun leuwih luhur henteu pasti ngahasilkeun kas leuwih luhur tina operasi. Data nempokeun arah nu kabalik: tina taun 2011 ka 2013, 'net income adjusted...' leungit tiap taun (tina $735.7 ka $598.4), sapertos 'net cash provided by operating activities' naék tiap taun (tina $273.5 ka $592.9). Ieu ngajelaskeun yén pangaruh perubahan dina working capital jeung item non-aktiva lianna nyababkeun pangaruh nu penting jeung makin saé dina arus kas.

question: Aya di antara kagiatan arus kas utama ('operating', 'investing', atawa 'financing') anu diwakilan ku baris data anu ngandung nilai positif jeung nilai negatip dina rentang tigatahun?
answer: net cash ( used in ) provided by financing activities
